	VIP $284.50 | A Seating $123.50 | B Seating $100.25 | C Seating $90.50 | D Seating $86.00<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Terrapin Station Entertainment and TEG Life Like Touring, in association with Universal Destinations and Experiences, present Gabby's Dollhouse Live! Presented by Walmart on tour from September 2025. In this a-MEOW-zing new live show, Gabby unboxes a special acorn that needs the magical touch of a rainbow to grow. But when CatRat causes a color cat-astrophe and breaks the rainbow, Gabby and the Gabby Cats must find the colors again to set things right. Gabby's Dollhouse Live! Presented by Walmart brings to life an original story featuring incredible puppets, dynamic staging, and songs that will have audiences singing and dancing along, from beginning to end. Tickets on sale now - sign up at www.gabbysdollhouselive.com for pre-sale access.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>CAT-TASTIC VIP EXPERIENCE<span><br/></span>Includes:<span><br/></span>• One (1) Premium Ticket to the Show*<span><br/></span>• Admission to the Gabby’s Dollhouse Live! Cat-tastic VIP Pre-Show Party**— Featuring coloring, stickers, temporary tattoos, and other hands-on fun!<span><br/></span>• One (1) Magical Meow Pass***<span><br/></span>• Character Greeting & Photo with Gabby (mascot) before the show****<span><br/></span>• Gabby’s VIP Goodie Set***<span><br/></span>• Themed Snacks & Refreshments<span><br/></span>• On-Site VIP Experience Host<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*Location provided at time of purchase<span><br/></span>** All ticket holders — both children & adults — must purchase a VIP Package to attend the VIP Party<span><br/></span>*** Provided at VIP check-in the night of the show<span><br/></span>****Please note that Character Greeting is with the Gabby costume character, not the actor from the TV show, or the actor performing in our stage show.
""";
