<http://www.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/event/28201ANLRQMDQPKBCRBQJSVDBPMCHQKNS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "SJTC: Come From Away";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Come From Away</h1><span><br/></span>Directed by Courtney and Tony LePage. Musical Direction by Michael Doherty.<span><br/></span>Original Broadway Production Produced by Junkyard Dog Productions.<span><br/></span>Orchestrations by August Eriksmoen. Arrangements by Ian Eisendrath.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Performances</h2><span><br/></span><ul><li>Wednesday, September 16, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Thursday, September 17, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Friday, September 18, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Saturday, September 19, 2026 at 2:00pm</li><li>Saturday, September 19, 2026 at 7:30pm</li><li>Sunday, September 20, 2026 at 2:00pm</li></ul><span><br/></span>Back by overwhelming demand, Come From Away is soaring across New Brunswick once again! Performed by an all–New Brunswick cast including Broadway’s own Tony LePage. This electrifying production is East Coast talent at its absolute best!<span><br/></span>Inspired by true events, this smash-hit musical tells the remarkable story of kindness in the days following September 11, when strangers became family in the small town of Gander, Newfoundland. Bursting with humour, heart, and unforgettable music, Come From Away is fast-paced, joyful, and deeply moving.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Funny, foot-stomping, and full of heart, this is the feel-good musical audiences can’t stop talking about. Proudly presented through a collaborative partnership between Saint John Theatre Company and Rogue Productions, Come From Away celebrates the power of community - onstage, offstage, and right here at home.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>COME FROM AWAY is presented through special arrangement with Music Theatre International (MTI). All authorized performance materials are also supplied by MTI. www.mtishows.com
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-09-16T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/files/b31927f9-5ae8-4fd0-812f-9bec84b81f49.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/location/201AGBHDRLQHNHPHKKMPKLGPMDRDTDMVL>;
