  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "SJTC: Frozen";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Frozen</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><span><br/></span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Experience the magic of Frozen! Join Anna, Elsa, Olaf, and friends on an electrifying, heart-melting adventure packed with unforgettable songs, dazzling magic, and a celebration of sisterhood that will have you laughing, crying, and cheering all the way to the final note.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><span><br/></span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Performances</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Wednesday, November 25th, 2026 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Thursday, November 26th, 2026 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Friday, November 26th, 2026 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Saturday, November 27th, 2026 at 2:00pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Saturday, November 27th, 2026 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase a <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.imperialtheatre.ca/fixedseries\">SJTC Subscription </a>and save 25% off single ticket prices!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We are happy to hold prior season subscribers' seats until September 1st 2026. Single tickets on sale September 1st 2026 at noon.
""";
