<http://www.spektrix.com/imperialtheatrenewbrunswick/event/42402ALJVDQKRMBQNJNNPRNKVBQCSLQML>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "SJTC: Spamalot";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Spamalot</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><span><br/></span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss Spamalot! A laugh-out-loud musical quest for the Holy Grail, where logic is optional and danger is rarely taken seriously. From “flesh wounds” that aren’t quite as bad as they look to gloriously absurd misadventures at every turn, it’s a fast-paced, joyfully ridiculous night at the theatre you won’t want to miss.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Performances</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Wednesday, May 19th, 2027 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Thursday, May 20th 2027 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Friday, May 21st, 2027 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Saturday, May 22nd, 2027 at 2:00pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>-Saturday, May 22nd, 2027 at 7:30pm<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase a <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://purchase.imperialtheatre.ca/fixedseries\">SJTC Subscription </a>and save 25% off single ticket prices!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We are happy to hold prior season subscribers' seats until September 1st 2026. Single tickets on sale September 1st, 2026 at noon.
""";
